<h2 id="languages">Language tools</h2>

<div>
<h3><a href="/languages/arabic/fuzzy/">Fuzzy Arabic Dictionary</a></h3>
<p>
  Look up Arabic words, even when you don't know how to spell them.
</p>

<div>
<h3><a href="/languages/egyptian/typewriter/">Hieroglyphic Egyptian Typewriter</a></h3>
<p>
  Type Manuel de Codage notation and see it rendered as hieroglyphs instantly.<br/>
  Includes a sign picker for quickly locating specific hieroglyphs.
</p>
</div>

<div>
<h3><a href="/languages/cantonese/correspondences/">Cantonese-Mandarin Sound Correspondences</a></h3>
